---application and middleware configuration
- intialize shibboleth idp 
- install passport saml package 
- configure saml strategy
- render idp metadata and copy ssl cert
- generate server ssl certs
- configure passport strategy attributes
- issuer is the service provider url :https://172.26.120.204/shibboleth
- enterypoint is the idp url : https://idp3-test.tu-dresden.de/idp/profile/SAML2/Redirect/SSO
- include certificates in the strategy attributes
- install phusion passenger
- add node appllication path to virtual host 
- add virtual host to apache config file 

---containerizing the app
- create a dockerfile
- create a github action to build and push image
- create docker compose file to pull and run a container from new image
